pageProduct.description:
Warnings

STORAGE:
Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.

WARNINGS:
Not recommended for use by pregnant and lactating women. For adult use only.

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:

  • One capsule daily, during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.
